# Tailwind CSS v4 (Scoped Notes)

## Context

- When working on Tailwind styling in this repo.

## Requirements

- Prefer Tailwind v4's CSS-first configuration (`@theme`) over a JavaScript-first config unless the repo still uses `@config` to import one.
- Use `@import "tailwindcss";` rather than `@tailwind base/components/utilities` when following v4 conventions.
